In this folder is all of the code and data needed to reproduce simulations from the paper:
Quantifying Metacognitive Thresholds Using Signal Detection Theory. Sherman M.T, Seth, A.K & Barrett A.B
This paper is currently uploaded as a pre-print on BioRxiv at https://doi.org/10.1101/361543

Hopefully the code is self-explanatory, but if you have any questions or comments please email me (Maxine Sherman)
at m.sherman@sussex.ac.uk
